			<Text>是的，我同意向你们的小战士们开放边境。</Text>
		</Row>
		<!--AI rejects from human-->
		<Row Tag="LOC_DIPLO_REJECT_OPEN_BORDERS_FROM_HUMAN_LEADER_GEDEMO_BISMARK_ANY" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
			<Text>我们目前不感兴趣。</Text>
		</Row>
		<!--AI requests from human-->
		<Row Tag="LOC_DIPLO_OPEN_BORDERS_FROM_AI_LEADER_GEDEMO_BISMARK_ANY" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
			<Text>你能允许我们的部队通过你的领土吗？</Text>
		</Row>
		<!--DECLARE FRIENDSHIP-->
		<!--AI accepts from human-->
		<Row Tag="LOC_DIPLO_ACCEPT_DECLARE_FRIEND_FROM_HUMAN_LEADER_GEDEMO_BISMARK_ANY" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
			<Text>我接受你的友谊。</Text>
		</Row>
		<!--AI Rejects from human -->
		<Row Tag="LOC_DIPLO_REJECT_DECLARE_FRIEND_FROM_HUMAN_LEADER_GEDEMO_BISMARK_ANY" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
			<Text>我拒绝如此荒谬的提议。</Text>
		</Row>
		<!--AI Requests friendship from human-->
		<Row Tag="LOC_DIPLO_DECLARE_FRIEND_FROM_AI_LEADER_GEDEMO_BISMARK_ANY" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
			<Text>仔细考虑一下这一友谊的提议吧，这对你很有好处。</Text>
		</Row>
		<!--Human accepts AI requests, AI responds-->
		<Row Tag="LOC_DIPLO_ACCEPT_DECLARE_FRIEND_FROM_AI_LEADER_GEDEMO_BISMARK_ANY" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
			<Text>谢谢你，朋友。</Text>
		</Row>
		<!--Human rejects AI requests, AI responds-->
		<Row Tag="LOC_DIPLO_REJECT_DECLARE_FRIEND_FROM_AI_LEADER_GEDEMO_BISMARK_ANY" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
			<Text>真失望。</Text>
		</Row>
		<!--ALLIANCE-->
		<!--AI Requests an alliance from human-->
